column1: EARTHTIME ID-TIMS DATA IMPORT TEMPLATE FOR TRIPOLI

column2: Enter date as mm/dd/yyyy in cell B10.
Enter Sample Name in cell B11.
Enter Fraction Name in cell B12.
Enter cycles per block in cell B13.  A zero denotes all data considered as a single block.
Name each column B16, C16, etc. with a ratio or function name such as 206/204.
Number cycles starting with 1 at row 17 and paste cycle data starting at cell B17.
